&nbsp;&nbsp;<i>17% to songs</i>
<br><b>Description:</b>&nbsp;Adds 17% to Percussion depending on song.
<br><b>Drop Location:</b><br>Drops in Mistmoore off Mynthi Davissi. Also drops other bard lutes - the Lute of the Gypsy Princess and a Gypsy Lute.
<br><b>Rarity:</b>&nbsp;Uncommon
<br><b>Level to Attain:</b>&nbsp;30<br><br><img src="/images/stats/imgStatsMMDrum.jpg" hspace="10" vspace="10"><br><br><b>How to Obtain this Item</b><br>This item is found in Mistmoore Castle inside the ballroom. Your invisibility song will aid you in getting there. It dops off a named gypsy - Mynthi Davissi, and is an enchanter around level 33, and will Charm your party so use any means to up your magic resistance. She stands in front of the piano, and you can see if she has the drum or the lute. She is surrounded by other gypsies, and at night these gypsies will respawn as werewolves.<br><br> Be careful of trains, these can run very rampant here.<br><br>&nbsp;<a href="/items.asp">Back to Items</a><br><br></td><td valign="top"><img src="/images/icons/imgIconDrum.jpg" align="right" hspace="10" vspace="10"><br clear="right"><br><span class="clsSmall"><b>Slot:</b><br>SECONDARY</span><br><span class="clsSmall"><b>Weight:</b>&nbsp;0.5</span>
